description:
Social epidemics behave in the same way that viral epidemics do. They are contagious, spread through small means and spill over into crisis mode as a result of a single dramatic event. Right now, the world is facing two pandemics. A viral one, Covid-19, and a social one, fear. Let's take a look at how we can respond to both these pandemics with hope.
